item.gtmthings.advanced_terminal.setting: Set the priority level for automatic coil placement.
Number of repetitions of the structure
Used to set the number of repetitions for the placement of repeating parts in structures like distillation towers, assembly lines, etc.

Whether to enable the no-Hatch mode (0: not enabled, 1: enabled)
After enabling the no-chamber mode, various Hatch will not be placed when they are not unique.

Whether to enable the coil-replace mode (0: not enabled, 1: enabled)
After enabling the coil-replace mode, coil will be replaced by the Coil before.

Whether to enable to use items in AE (0: not enabled, 1: enabled)
After enabling this, you can autobuild with items in AE storage by an ME terminal.
